### Get Cart
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Add to Cart
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/cart/add
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}

### Update Cart Item
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/v1/cart/item/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 3
}

### Remove Cart Item
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/v1/cart/item/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Clear Cart
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/v1/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
